# Python-generated files
__pycache__/
*.py[oc]
build/
dist/
wheels/
*.egg-info

# Virtual environments
.venv

# macOS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
*.swp

# Runtime data & backups (live in home or are regenerated)
.mlx-backups/
Scroll/build/
**/build/Build/

# Stray local captures
Screenshot*.png

# Nested clone of the GitHub repo — not part of this tree
ScrollMLX/

# Agent work products — NEVER part of the product source. Ad-hoc/project work now
# writes to ~/ScrollProjects/* (outside this repo); these are belt-and-suspenders for
# anything that still lands at the root, plus a parking spot for throwaway test output.
scratch/
scroll-artifacts/
# Any markdown the agent drops at the REPO ROOT is throwaway test output — ignore it,
# but keep the real top-level docs. (docs/*.md are unaffected — only root-level matches.)
/*.md
!/README.md
!/CONTRIBUTING.md
# stray non-md test output seen at the root
tip_splitter.py

# CodeMie is EPAM-private — it must NEVER be published to this public repo. It lives as a
# runtime plugin (~/.scroll/provider-plugins/codemie.md) and is shared via git.epam.com.
# Belt-and-suspenders: ignore any CodeMie plugin/setup artifact that lands in the tree.
**/codemie*.md
**/codemie-setup.command

# Xcode per-user state
**/xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate

# JS test deps
node_modules/
